                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-10-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 19, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Dawson states that he arrived in the afternoon of the 18th and formally
                    visited Provisional President on the 19th; that his reception by the President
                    and cabinet was most cordial.</p>
            </div>
